mention.text: The opinions expressed in this commentary
-LRB- CNN -RRB- -- Three weeks ago , I had the privilege of visiting our civilian leaders and military commanders , as well as our troops , in Afghanistan .
my fourth trip to the country
Ambassador James Cunningham and General Joseph F. Dunford
the Afghan people , security forces and government
the Afghan people and its security forces
the resolve to complete its task
The biggest takeaway from my visit
the gains we have made together
the blood of our fellow citizens
